fields.name: Accurate IV Checkers
fields.value:
Tap here to find the exact IV for your Pokémon.
[PokemonGO Hub on Therian Tornadus](https://db.pokemongohub.net/pokemon/641/iv-chart)

**or download an IV checker app for your phone**
[PokeGenie - iOS and Android](http://www.pokegenie.net/)
[CalcyIV - Android Only](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tesmath.calcy&hl=en_US&gl=US)

fields.name: Disclaimer
fields.value:
Actual IV's percentages vary depending upon stat distribution. 

*The IV's listed above are for non-powered up Pokémon and are generic ranges.  There are circumstances that a Pokémon's CP could be in those ranges and have a higher or lower IV percentage.*
